- [ ] Alerts shown prominently in watch output
- [ ] --alert-bell triggers terminal bell
- [ ] --alert-command runs custom command on alert
- [ ] Alert cooldown prevents spam
- [ ] Recovery clears alert state (can re-alert)

## Testing Strategy
- Test threshold detection at various levels
- Test bell character output
- Test custom command with env vars
- Test cooldown rate limiting
